<section id="budget" class="bg-[#111111] text-white font-poppins px-4 py-8 max-w-full">
    <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-4 px-4" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold">Solicite um <span class="text-orange-500">Orçamento</span></h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-base md:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Preencha o formulário abaixo com as informações da sua demanda. Quanto mais detalhes, mais rápido conseguimos retornar.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-8" data-aos="zoom-in">
        <form class="bg-black rounded-lg p-6 flex flex-col gap-4 text-sm" action="#" method="POST">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                <label class="font-semibold" for="name">Nome <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                <input type="text" name="name" required class="p-2 rounded bg-gray-800 border border-transparent text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-orange-500 focus:border-2"/>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                <label class="font-semibold" for="phone">WhatsApp <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                <input type="text" name="phone" required class="p-2 rounded bg-gray-800 border border-transparent text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-orange-500 focus:border-2"/>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                <label class="font-semibold" for="email">Email <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                <input type="email" name="email" required class="p-2 rounded bg-gray-800 border border-transparent text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-orange-500 focus:border-2"/>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                <label class="font-semibold" for="description">Descrição <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                <textarea name="description" rows="5" required class="p-2 rounded bg-gray-800 border border-transparent text-white resize-none focus:outline-none focus:border-orange-500 focus:border-2"></textarea>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs leading-snug">Descreva exatamente o que você precisa. Quanto mais claro, mais rápido será o nosso retorno. Evite informações vagas para não atrasar o processo.</p>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="mt-2 bg-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-600 transition text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded w-max">
                Enviar
                <i class="fas fa-paper-plane ml-1"></i> 
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>
</section>
